$interpreted: Sanchez: Fool! Don't let anyone touch that! That's worth more than your life!
Rune: ...I'll be...careful.
City Guard: Passage Permit.
Sanchez: Huh? I swear I put it right here...
City Guard: What's going on?
Sanchez: ...Hmph!
Sanchez: We're with Priest Yusuf. There's no need for a passage permit. If we're delayed, are you willing to take the blame?
City Guard: You think you can just barge in here without a passage permit? How do I know you're not a smuggler? Let's take a look!
Rune: Sanchez said...don't touch...!
Sanchez: Don't come any closer! I'm the High Priest Devious'...humble servant. If you cross me, you cross the High Priest!
City Guard: Damn...if I cross the High Priest, it will definitely cause trouble for General Lazer...
Lazer: ...You're with High Priest Devious. So what?
City Guard: General Lazer!
Lazer: Queen Diana demands that the kingdom's laws be upheld. Arrest them immediately.
Devious: Hsssss...General Lazer, I see you haven't changed. Unable to understand the importance of social relationships.
Female Civilian: Wow! Someone from the Holy Shrine!
Child: The High Priest!
Civilian: Look! The High Priest himself! Amazing!
Devious: General Lazer, let them go.
Lazer: They don't have passage permits, and they're using your name to threaten the guards.
Lazer: So the High Priest has no need to obey Her Majesty's laws?
Devious: I wouldn't dare. I'm just afraid the General misunderstood. Oh, look! What's this?
Sanchez: Oh, a passage permit!
Devious: Hsssss...next time remember to put it somewhere safe.
Lazer: ……
Devious: General Lazer, Queen Diana wouldn't want her people to be punished simply because they misplaced their passage permit, would she?
Lazer: ......
Lazer: Looks like the High Priest won this time. Let them pass.
Yusuf: Fools! Attracting the attention of Lazer!
Sanchez: Master, don't worry. With the High Priest on our side there's nothing to fear.
Yusuf: What did you say? You think you can give the High Priest orders!? You misplaced your passage permit. You might as well have lost your brain!
Yusuf: Enough, I'm tired. My hand is getting numb...
Yusuf: Pick up the staff!
Yusuf: Beat him! Harder! Beat him until he can no longer move!
Rune: Command...received.
Sanchez: Ah! Ahhhh!
Yusuf: Good! Don't be a baby. We'll bring a doctor in here when it's all over.
Sanchez: Finally. Any longer and I'd be dead...
Rune: Master said...beat you until...you can't move.
Sanchez: Scum! What are you doing!? Can't you see the master left?
Rune: ...This...is...master's...orders...
Sanchez: You have got to be kidding!? Wait a second! Ouch! Oww!
